        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 6:22-28",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), and of Merari (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 6:29-30",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "); and (b) the genealogies of David's chief musicians (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 6:31",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 6:32",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), of Heman the Kohathite (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 6:33-38",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), of Asaph the Gershonite (",
        "children": []
      },
